---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const canonicalURL = new URL("/about", Astro.site);
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About taeglich"
  description="A quiet practice, one day at a time."
  renderH1={false}
  canonicalURL={canonicalURL}
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p
        class="mb-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-500 uppercase"
      >
        About
      </p>
      <h1
        class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
      >
        One finished artifact, every day.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        taeglich is a daily practice of shipping small, complete web pieces.
        Each artifact belongs to a date and is treated as frozen once shipped.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-10 border-t border-gray-100 pt-10 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Why it exists</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          The project values consistency over scale: a rhythm of finishing,
          letting each day stand on its own, and moving forward without
          revisiting yesterday unless something is truly broken.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">How it works</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          Every artifact is scoped to be done. Minimal scripting, static-first
          rendering, and a deliberate visual choice for the dayâ€™s theme.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-100 pt-10">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Principles</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-4 text-sm text-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-gray-500 uppercase">
            Finish
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Each day is a complete artifact, not a sketch.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-gray-500 uppercase">
            Freeze
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">Shipped days remain as they were.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-gray-500 uppercase">
            Vary
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Each day can change tone, layout, and interaction.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-wide text-gray-500 uppercase">
            Respect
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Accessibility and performance are part of correctness.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-100 pt-10">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Availability</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        This page is intentionally unlinked. It exists quietly for those who
        find it, and it lives alongside the artifacts without calling attention
        to itself.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
